name: Verify Program , Market Segment and Entity ID columns are shown in all reports for Quote Overview

testSteps.description: 1: Verify Program , Market Segment and Entity ID columns are shown in all reports for Quote Overview ({Reports=Quotes Pending Issuance})

children.description: Given underwriter is on home page of PAS
And select Reports 'Quotes Pending Issuance' from Quotes
When user navigates to the filter edits screen

Then below fields should be visible
| Program |
| Market Segment |
| Entity ID |
